s0362: Chu minister Shen Bao Xu came to seek urgent help, seven days without eating, day and night weeping.
s0363: Therefore Qin sent 500 chariots to rescue Chu, defeated the Wu army.
s0364: The Wu army returned, Chu King Zhao was then able to re-enter Ying.
s0365: Duke Ai ascended for thirty-six years, died.
s0366: Crown prince Yi Gong, Yi Gong died early, could not ascend, established Yi Gong's son, this was Duke Hui.
s0367: Duke Hui of Qin first year, Confucius acted as prime minister of Lu.
s0368: Fifth year, Jin ministers Zhonghang and Fan clans rebelled against Jin, Jin sent Zhi clan and Zhao Jian Zi to attack them, Fan and Zhonghang clans fled to Qi.
s0369: Duke Hui ascended for ten years, died, his son Duke Dao ascended.
s0370: Duke Dao second year, Qi minister Tian Qi assassinated his lord Ruzi, established his elder brother Yang Sheng, this was Duke Dao.
s0371: Sixth year, Wu defeated Qi army.
s0372: Qi people assassinated Duke Dao, established his son Duke Jian.
s0373: Duke Dao of Qin ninth year, Duke Dao died, his son Duke Ling ascended.
s0374: Duke Ling of Qin first year, attacked the Quanrong.
s0387: Fourteenth year, Duke Ling died, his son Duke Jian ascended.
s0388: Duke Jian of Qin first year, attacked the Quanrong.
s0400: Thirteenth year, Duke Jian died, his son Duke Huiwen ascended.
s0401: Duke Huiwen of Qin first year, attacked the Quanrong.
